      • overrides

        public final KafkaCollector.Builder overrides​(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,?> overrides)
        By default, a consumer will be built from properties derived from builder defaults, as well "auto.offset.reset" -> "smallest". Any properties set here will override the consumer config.

        For example: Only consume spans since you connected by setting the below. 

        
 Map<String, String> overrides = new LinkedHashMap<>();
 overrides.put(ConsumerConfig.AUTO_OFFSET_RESET_CONFIG, "largest");
 builder.overrides(overrides);
        See Also:
        ConsumerConfig
